to know you, Mr. Tolson.

447
00:26:17,589 --> 00:26:19,352
l'm not the one on the debate team.

448
00:26:19,424 --> 00:26:21,892
Are we not engaged
in a debate right now?

449
00:26:23,028 --> 00:26:25,258
All right.

450
