controlling their slaves,

470
00:27:16,481 --> 00:27:19,939
so they sent for Mr. Lynch
to teach them his methods.

471
00:27:20,052 --> 00:27:23,544
The word ''lynching''
came from his last name.

472
00:27:23,655 --> 00:27:27,853
His methods were very simple,
but they were diabolical.

473
00:27:27,926 --> 00:27:31,987
Keep the slave physically strong
but psychologically weak

474
00:27:32,064 --> 00:27:33,759
and dependent on the slave master.

475
00:27:33,832 --> 00:27:37,233
Keep the body, take the mind.

476
00:27:38,770 --> 00:27:43,867
l...and every other
professor on this campus

477
00:27:43,942 --> 00:27:46,570
are here to help you...

478
00:27:48,413 --> 00:27:51,382
to find, take back,

479
00:27:51,450 --> 00:27:55,819
and keep your righteous mind...

480
00:27:55,887 --> 00:27:59,550
because obviously you have lost it.

481
00:28:01,460 --> 00:28:04,156
That's all you need to know about me,
Mr. Lowe.

482
00:28:07,933 --> 00:28:09,525
Class dismissed.

483
